{{ChacoAR-geo-stub}}

The [[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation (BBC)]] occupies many properties in the [[United Kingdom]], and occupied many other in previous years. The headquarters of the corporation is [[Broadcasting House]] in London; with many other divisions located in London and around the UK. Since 2007 the BBC has been developing a significant base at [[MediaCityUK]] in Salford, to which it has relocated several departments. There are also production bases in Belfast, Birmingham, Bristol, Cardiff and Glasgow. The BBC also owns news bureaux and relay stations outside the UK.
